items.value: One of our best teachers in our schoolhouse! Not only that he knows where you are at all times, but can also corner you perfectly!
Hello there! Welcome to my Fun Schoolhouse.
I think you are smarter than me!

Fire Extinguisher
A somewhat powerful extinguisher
that can make Foxo frustrated, and also mad!

Water Bucket Of Water
It's a bucket that contains water,
spilling it will cause vulnerable people to not walk into that path.
The spill lasts 10 seconds so use it wisely!
